@font-face {
    font-family: 'Roboto';
    src: local('Roboto Black'), local('Roboto-Black'),
        url(data:application/font-woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff2');
    font-weight: 900;
    font-style: normal;
    font-display: swap;
}

@font-face {
    font-family: 'Roboto';
    src: local('Roboto Medium'), local('Roboto-Medium'),
        url(data:application/font-woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff2');
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: normal;
    font-display: swap;
}

@font-face {
    font-family: 'Roboto';
    src: local('Roboto'), local('Roboto-Regular'),
        url(data:application/font-woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,) format('woff2');
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;
    font-display: swap;
}
